        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43382472/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43382472/" class="">第105页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4145813/" class=" " title="风间天马">风间天马</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43382472">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">传统民主概念的虚假在于他没有认识到局内人与局外人之间的根本差别。它误入歧途的原因是希望局外人也能像局内人那样处理实质性问题，他做不到。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-25 15:40</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>传统民主概念的虚假在于他没有认识到局内人与局外人之间的根本差别。它误入歧途的原因是希望局外人也能像局内人那样处理实质性问题，他做不到。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
